Package org.livingdoc.converters.time

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTemporalConverter<T extends Temporal>
    The AbstractTemporalConverter is the abstraction of the time converters.
    LocalDateConverter
    This converter parses a String to the local date format
    LocalDateTimeConverter
    This converter parses a String to the local date and time format
    LocalTimeConverter
    This converter parses a String to the local time format
    OffsetDateTimeConverter
    This converter parses a String to the time format with offset from UTC
    ZonedDateTimeConverter
    This converter parses a String to the time format with offset from UTC and a zone configuration regarding summer time
